Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 120 - The Beautiful World: Episode 20
articles.description: Japan throws a swanky party to celebrate his alliance with Germany and Italy. Germany wants to get down to business, but Italy is looking forward to snacks, calico kittens, and bath time!

articles.title: Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 117 - The Beautiful World: Episode 17
articles.description: When the countries gather to show off their favorite horror movies, it’s nothing but boobs, bloody entrails, Japanese ghosts, creepy naked Santas, and mental stabbings! OMG WHAT WAS THAT NOISE!?

articles.title: Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 110 - The Beautiful World: Episode 10
articles.description: Young Greece waxes philosophical about his love of cats, his desire to pet cats, and his hunger for sweets. Then he takes a bath with Turkey. Turkey is super cool. And strong.

articles.title: Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 109 - The Beautiful World: Episode 9
articles.description: Belgium wants to throw a waffle party, but the only things her big bro Netherlands cares about are pickled fish, clean kitchens, and cold hard cash! He so blunt - and dreamy!

articles.title: Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 107 - The Beautiful World: Episode 7
articles.description: In today’s episode: Quality time in the bathtub. Also, America’s got some pretty sweet dance moves. Japan’s got some pretty sweet abs. And why am I just now hearing about this cat that apparently likes to sit in pots?

articles.title: Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 103 - The Beautiful World: Episode 3
articles.description: It seems W Academy’s most ridiculous clubs each share the same single member. This member’s identity should not surprise you. Also, HUGE news! A NEVER-BEFORE-SEEN character shows up around two minutes into the episode!

articles.title: Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 112 - The Beautiful World: Episode 12
articles.description: Japan’s peaceful soak in a nice, hot tub is ruined when America kicks in the window and invites him to a Halloween party – in his room! Also, England summons an old fairy to scare the pants off America. Scary no pants time!

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 98 - World Series: Episode 46
articles.description: America travels to the land of Japan in order to become friends with some whales - or something like that. Anyway, when the boys from the west come ashore in the east, awkwardness and tea drinking ensues.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 91 - World Series: Episode 39
articles.description: Stunning developments concerning Hungary’s ample front are revealed, and disaster ensues when Italy borrows Germany’s car without asking!

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 89 - World Series: Episode 37
articles.description: A mysterious encounter in the falling snow only leads to more mysteries. How mysterious, right? Later, Italy gets punched in the stomach and Russia eats the end of the episode! Also - CAT STAMPEDE.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 86 - World Series: Episode 34
articles.description: Germany explains why he’s always able to stop England from escaping the Italian prison. Of course, after Germany explains it all, England might have a better chance of finally getting away. Meanwhile, ROCKET PUNCH!

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 85 - World Series: Episode 33
articles.description: England gets a new wardrobe and some shiny shoes. He looks pretty slick, but there’s no guarantee that his new duds will help him get across the border. Later in the episode, the world comes to an end - unless it doesn’t!

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 129 - The World Twinkle: Episode 9
articles.description: Sealand goes out on an adventure with Seborga and Wy to find new friends.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 84 - World Series: Episode 32
articles.description: Sealand’s trying to make friends, but he might be too pushy to pull it off. Meanwhile, England manages to escape an Italian prison, only to end up in the hands of Germany! Speaking of Germany, did you know he has a dog?

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 82 - World Series: Episode 30
articles.description: It’s time for another G8 meeting! While America thinks it might be time to lose a member or two, France wants to bring Spain into the fold. Later, kitty Japan adorably expresses his adorable love of tuna. Simply adorable!

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 93 - World Series: Episode 41
articles.description: In today’s fashion-centric episode, England is uncomfortable with France’s willingness to dress in girly clothes. Later, England’s awkward feelings only multiply when codpieces come into style.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 77 - World Series: Episode 25
articles.description: Poor Spain gets chewed out for spending too much money on his mission to bring Romano back. When the little guy hears how much trouble the big guy’s in, he pays him a bedroom visit to offer his thanks.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 70 - World Series: Episode 18
articles.description: Sweden has a way of making people feel weird. Just ask Estonia and Latvia. And Poland. And the customers at his café. And everyone ever. Just ask anyone!

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 66 - World Series: Episode 14
articles.description: America is psyched when a UFO crashes at his place! He makes the acquaintance of the vessel’s pilot and introduces him to England - who makes a less-than-stellar impression on the interstellar traveler.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 76 - World Series: Episode 24
articles.description: Turkey seems unstoppable and Chibi Romano is powerless in his clutches! When Spain arrives to save the little guy, Turkey decides to return home - but not before issuing an ominous warning.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 65 - World Series: Episode 13
articles.description: Austria’s losing big time, and all appears lost until Hungary arrives to help! She’s got 100,000 battle-ready soldiers with her - and a seriously crazy look in her eyes.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 60 - World Series: Episode 8
articles.description: Germany, struggling to understand Italy, makes an entry in his diary detailing the little pasta-freak’s every move. Also, back when he had long hair, Germany totally looked like a rock star.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 57 - World Series: Episode 5
articles.description: Poor England is suffering from a nasty cold. Meanwhile, Lithuania reflects on his complicated past with Poland, who doesn’t seem to be taking the Russian threat very seriously.

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 134 - The World Twinkle: Episode 14
articles.description: Canada and his neighbor America. Many people think they look alike, but what about their personalities?

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 59 - World Series: Episode 7
articles.description: Late at night, Hungary has a vision: God appears before her and sends her to smack France in the head with a frying pan. Speaking of France, in this episode he teaches Italy a little bit about the birds and the bees.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 55 - World Series: Episode 3
articles.description: Japan is still hanging out with Greece, who admits that he dreams of being resurrected as a cat. It truly is a touching moment - until Turkey shows up.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 54 - World Series: Episode 2
articles.description: In this episode, Chibitalia + Cat Festival = Ridiculously adorable. Meanwhile, Japan spends some time getting to know his mysterious new buddy, Greece.

articles.title: Hetalia: World Series - Episode 63 - World Series: Episode 11
articles.description: Japan’s electronic gadgets are really selling well, but he’s falling behind in manufacturing. China seems to think he can help. Later, it becomes clear that Japan might be spending a little too much time with Italy!

articles.title: Hetalia: Axis Powers - Episode 42 - Axis Powers: Episode 42
articles.description: Russia introduces the world to his sisters, the busty, bouncy Ukraine and the very intense Belarus. It’s an unusual family, to say the least.

articles.title: Hetalia: Axis Powers - Episode 37 - Axis Powers: Episode 37
articles.description: Russia’s heading over to Germany’s place for a sleepover, and he’s worried about what to wear. Italy’s got some concerns, too. If his friends make new friends, will he be pushed aside?

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 121 - The World Twinkle: Episode 1
articles.description: The G8 nation-cats gather again today to discuss household policies as well as the trading of canned cat food.

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 131 - The World Twinkle: Episode 11
articles.description: Little America becomes friends with a boy named Davie.

articles.title: Hetalia: Axis Powers - Episode 46 - Axis Powers: Episode 46
articles.description: U.K. develops a serious case of hair envy - and an aversion to scissors - in the wake of another humiliating encounter with France and his gorgeous, golden locks.

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 126 - The World Twinkle: Episode 6
articles.description: As usual, Italy is sobbing and calling Germany for help. What trouble is he in this time?

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 135 - The World Twinkle: Episode 15
articles.description: While waiting at camp, Italy tells Germany that he’s bored and wants to try acupressure.

articles.title: Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 118 - The Beautiful World: Episode 18
articles.description: The dreamy boys of Hetalia love horror films! Canada’s opus features a cage full of pancakes and bears, Germany shows off its jugs and vampires, and America proves that a good cook can kill any zombie! Hold up – who in the eff is this Canada dude!?

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 121 - The World Twinkle: Episode 1
articles.description: The G8 nation-cats gather again today to discuss household policies as well as the trading of canned cat food.

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 134 - The World Twinkle: Episode 14
articles.description: Canada and his neighbor America. Many people think they look alike, but what about their personalities?

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 131 - The World Twinkle: Episode 11
articles.description: Little America becomes friends with a boy named Davie.

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 125 - The World Twinkle: Episode 5
articles.description: While England is fighting in Africa, America comes to help him.

articles.title: Hetalia: The World Twinkle - Episode 124 - The World Twinkle: Episode 4
articles.description: Finland introduces the Nordic states. Meanwhile, Estonia asks his buddy Finland to help him become part of the Nordic states.

articles.title: Hetalia: The Beautiful World - Episode 111 - The Beautiful World: Episode 11
articles.description: It’s April Fools’ Day and someone is forcing all the countries to dress up in embarrassing costumes! France is suddenly super small, and everyone is up in arms! Except that one guy who lives upstairs from America. I can never remember his name.
